{"tid":2055801,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［煲底］有啲嘢點到即止就好","createTime":"2020-06-08T08:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T10:38:10.000Z","uid":351252,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ff1f63b602aff6159bc7c49dada3de3e319bfbc0","tid":2055801,"uid":351252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:34:59.000Z","msg":"一起身見到個friend send俾我睇<br />\n 睇到嗰下心諗癡L咗邊條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個人認為黃店唔係旨在話俾人知老細同啲店員有幾黃，而係一種政治與良知上嘅取態，俾返啲客人自己去選擇。<br />\n坦白講我睇到嗰下係躁咗，名黃裝修黃，連碟肥牛都要插支旗仔，約人去「煲底」打邊爐講句「煲底見」，望住幅牆上面嘅同路人，到底要啲人開心食定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定其實只係一種自high覺得滿足咗好黃店feel嘅心理感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n君不見大把黃店都係低調黃，唔會用「黃」作為gimmick，因為呢場運動實在太多傷心嘢，拎呢樣嘢嚟做gimmick真係over咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />店主未必係想借個光環做生意，但成件事真係over咗，同埋有啲自high嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預咗可能有人會話我分化，話唔准批評黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%85%B2%E5%BA%95-%E6%98%AF%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E7%9B%BC%E5%BE%85-%E5%80%9F%E4%BD%9C%E6%8B%9B%E5%BE%A0%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%BD%E4%B8%BB%E6%84%8F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2585%25B2%25E5%25BA%2595-%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%259B%25BC%25E5%25BE%2585-%25E5%2580%259F%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%25BE%25A0%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%2584%258F%2F&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=a1700795\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%2585%25B2%25E5%25BA%2595-%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%259B%25BC%25E5%25BE%2585-%25E5%2580%259F%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%258B%259B%25E5%25BE%25A0%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%